{
  "stem": "23155.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the beginning of February, we walked out from-- from the factory to the entrance to the camp, and the sirens went for the air raid.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had a German guard with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We called him Pappie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was nicely rotund.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was-- he was a nice guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He never-- they had to wear a gas mask, but they never had a gas mask in it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had all kinds of other things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They might have an apple in it, a little piece of bread or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So Pappie was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it was, you see, when there's an-- an attack, there's-- they call it fore alarm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That means before the attack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That means when-- when the planes cross the Channel and came to the land, to Europe, to the mainland, then it became a fore alarm.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That means now they're really here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the second time, the sirens went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so we wanted to go in, and they said no, that we can't go in because they have to count us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And next to me was a girl by the name of Suzie Glazer, and she was carrying a pail of water.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because we changed every day, somebody else, so we could wash in warm water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And as we were standing there waiting to be let in, the air raid started.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So the gates open, we started to run.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I ran through the dining hall out the back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we got-- they really let us have it but real good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Pappie was killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Suzie Glazer was killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I don't know how many girls were killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There were some wounded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The-- Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Gold, she was our physician, she was wounded.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I landed in the back of the dining hall outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
